590
00:21:02,210 --> 00:21:04,110
- No, I think...
- It's too youthful. Forget it.

591
00:21:07,450 --> 00:21:09,220
Ms. Zhou, how about the black one?

592
00:21:09,450 --> 00:21:10,660
The black one...

593
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:13,690
Black is safe.

594
00:21:13,690 --> 00:21:14,650
