605
00:21:31,650 --> 00:21:32,940
Why are you so nervous?

606
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:34,730
Am I nervous?

607
00:21:34,730 --> 00:21:35,570
Am I?

608
00:21:35,690 --> 00:21:36,530
Aren't you?

609
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:38,110
No.

610
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:40,210
I'm not nervous
about going to his place.

611
00:21:40,210 --> 00:21:41,730
How about this outfit? Will it work?

612
00:21:41,730 --> 00:21:43,450
This one is better. This is better.

613
00:21:43,450 --> 00:21:44,840
- Look at it.
- Wait.

614
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:45,680
Help me out.

615
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:47,250
My hand hurts. It's killing me.

616
00:21:47,250 --> 00:21:48,390
Put the patch on for me.

617
00:21:48,890 --> 00:21:50,050
You've overworked

618
00:21:50,050 --> 00:21:51,600
your hand

619
00:21:51,600 --> 00:21:52,890
preparing for New Year's.

620
00:21:52,890 --> 00:21:54,120
- Help me.
- How about this?

621
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:55,010
I'll change.

622
00:21:55,010 --> 00:21:56,360
I'll change. Take a look for me.

623
00:21:56,360 --> 00:21:57,500
No need to change.

624
00:21:57,690 --> 00:21:59,650
You're beautiful.
Anything you wear looks good.

625
00:21:59,650 --> 00:22:01,390
Help me with the patch.

626
00:22:04,520 --> 00:22:05,410
Tomorrow,

627
00:22:05,410 --> 00:22:07,460
it'll be great not having
to do any dishes.

628
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:08,970
(Tang Yang)

629
00:22:08,970 --> 00:22:09,840
Can I take that

630
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:10,830
