631
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:11,840
(Jiang Shiyan)

632
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:12,680
Of course.

633
00:22:12,930 --> 00:22:14,400
Even though Ms. Zhou complains

634
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:15,410
that we're always

635
00:22:15,410 --> 00:22:17,070
making trouble,

636
00:22:17,490 --> 00:22:18,930
I think deep down

637
00:22:18,930 --> 00:22:20,220
(Tang Yang)
she enjoys it.

638
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:21,880
And you?

639
00:22:22,380 --> 00:22:23,600
(Shiyan)
Do you enjoy it?

640
00:22:38,490 --> 00:22:40,150
You've said everything.

641
00:22:40,340 --> 00:22:42,820
(Tang Yang)

642
00:22:54,210 --> 00:22:55,360
We borrowed a big car

643
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:56,320
