644
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:57,630
This trip is all thanks to you.

645
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:59,490
It's New Year's after all. Right?

646
00:22:59,490 --> 00:23:01,390
My sister is always so thoughtful.

647
00:23:02,860 --> 00:23:03,860
(Jiang Shiyan)

648
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:08,280
Hey, Jiang Shiyan, what's up?

649
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:09,220
Hey, Yang.

650
00:23:09,600 --> 00:23:11,280
We just picked up my aunt

651
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:12,500
