652
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:15,350
My grandpa fell today.

653
00:23:16,690 --> 00:23:18,210
What happened? Is it serious?

654
00:23:18,210 --> 00:23:19,150
When did it happen?

655
00:23:19,930 --> 00:23:20,940
Just this morning.

656
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:22,600
We just finished X-rays

657
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:23,440
at the hospital.

658
00:23:24,080 --> 00:23:25,120
The doctor said it's okay,

659
00:23:25,120 --> 00:23:26,070
but he'll be monitored.

660
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:28,180
We wanted him to stay in the hospital,

661
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:29,790
but he insisted on going home.

662
00:23:30,450 --> 00:23:31,530
It's New Year's.

663
00:23:31,530 --> 00:23:32,730
Who wants to stay in hospital?

664
00:23:32,730 --> 00:23:33,570
Exactly.

665
00:23:34,490 --> 00:23:35,940
Where are you now?

666
00:23:36,930 --> 00:23:37,770
I just

