00:23:38,250 --> 00:23:39,150
got home.

668
00:23:44,250 --> 00:23:45,940
We might not be able to make it

669
00:23:46,250 --> 00:23:47,310
to the hotel today.

670
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:51,490
But I've arranged everything

671
00:23:51,490 --> 00:23:52,590
for dinner.

672
00:23:53,040 --> 00:23:54,210
Could you please apologize

673
00:23:54,210 --> 00:23:55,650
