674
00:23:55,650 --> 00:23:56,730
We agreed on this earlier,

675
00:23:56,730 --> 00:23:57,570
but there's no way

676
00:23:57,930 --> 00:23:59,150
we can make it back.

677
00:23:59,930 --> 00:24:01,730
We're family. No need to apologize.

678
00:24:01,730 --> 00:24:03,120
- Right.
- As long as he's okay.

679
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:04,550
Yeah, his health is the priority.

680
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:06,650
Take care of your grandpa

681
00:24:06,650 --> 00:24:07,900
and Aunt Yi.

682
00:24:08,360 --> 00:24:09,790
Thanks, Aunt. Thanks, Ms. Zhou.

683
00:24:10,410 --> 00:24:12,450
Enjoy your time and have fun.

684
00:24:12,450 --> 00:24:13,360
I'll send the QR code

685
00:24:13,360 --> 00:24:14,390
for the voucher to Tang.

686
00:24:15,800 --> 00:24:16,730
Alright, rest assured.

687
00:24:16,730 --> 00:24:17,700
Don't worry about us.

688
00:24:36,890 --> 00:24:38,490
Happy New Year. You're back.

689
00:24:38,490 --> 00:24:40,030
- Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year.

690
00:24:40,450 --> 00:24:41,900
Little one, Happy New Year.

691
00:24:42,490 --> 00:24:43,390
Happy New Year.

692
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:47,940
