696
00:24:54,690 --> 00:24:55,530
I'm not using it.

697
00:24:56,250 --> 00:24:57,350
I said I wouldn't use it.

698
00:24:58,450 --> 00:24:59,590
Today,

699
00:24:59,730 --> 00:25:00,790
you'll use it

700
00:25:00,970 --> 00:25:02,390
whether you want to or not.

701
00:25:03,210 --> 00:25:05,890
The doctor told you to stay
in the hospital, but you refused.

702
00:25:05,890 --> 00:25:07,080
He told you to stay in bed,

703
00:25:07,080 --> 00:25:08,150
and you refused either.

704
00:25:09,210 --> 00:25:10,460
Is your foot swollen?

705
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:12,420
Is it as swollen
as a little steamed bun?

706
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:14,180
How can you write the couplets?

707
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:15,930
Are you 80

708
00:25:15,930 --> 00:25:16,790
or 8 years old?

709
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:18,120
