710
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:19,220
Integrity.

711
00:25:19,600 --> 00:25:21,110
Do you understand integrity?

712
00:25:21,650 --> 00:25:22,940
I promised them.

713
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:24,070
I have to keep my word.

714
00:25:24,600 --> 00:25:26,800
I write the New Year's couplets
for the village

715
00:25:26,800 --> 00:25:27,900
every year.

716
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:29,400
I don't care.

717
00:25:29,650 --> 00:25:31,260
I don't care about your couplets.

718
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:34,220
Why don't you try persuading them?

719
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:35,880
I can't.

720
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:38,180
Uncle, you're older.

721
00:25:38,360 --> 00:25:39,200
You go.

722
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:40,690
I wouldn't dare.

723
00:25:40,690 --> 00:25:41,980
I'm afraid of your mom.

724
00:25:42,600 --> 00:25:43,590
Is this the place?

725
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:45,690
Yeah, this is it. I remember

726
00:25:45,690 --> 00:25:46,890
