727
00:25:46,890 --> 00:25:47,730
This is the one.

728
00:25:47,970 --> 00:25:48,940
Jiang Shiyan.

729
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,160
Jiang Shiyan.

730
00:25:52,250 --> 00:25:53,090
Yang.

731
00:25:53,970 --> 00:25:54,810
Tang.

732
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:55,870
- You're here.
- Uncle.

733
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:56,920
Ms. Zhou, hello.

734
00:25:57,010 --> 00:25:58,390
Happy New Year.

735
00:25:59,560 --> 00:26:00,800
Weren't you going to the hotel?

736
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:01,640
Why did you come?

737
00:26:02,360 --> 00:26:04,730
Well, Ms. Zhou said we planned

738
00:26:04,730 --> 00:26:06,760
