741
00:26:09,250 --> 00:26:10,690
So, we packed up the dinner

742
00:26:10,690 --> 00:26:11,600
and came here

743
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:12,700
to spend it with you.

744
00:26:13,010 --> 00:26:13,980
Welcome, welcome.

745
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:15,700
Come in, come in.

746
00:26:18,410 --> 00:26:19,280
Uncle.

747
00:26:19,280 --> 00:26:20,410
Happy New Year.

748
00:26:20,410 --> 00:26:22,690
- Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year.

749
00:26:22,690 --> 00:26:24,600
Take these things.

750
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:25,770
This year feels special.

751
00:26:25,770 --> 00:26:26,930
Happy New Year.

752
00:26:26,930 --> 00:26:28,660
