753
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:31,120
Yes, yes, the dinner.

754
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:32,070
Just need to heat it up.

755
00:26:32,890 --> 00:26:34,390
That's a figurine for your cousin,

756
00:26:34,520 --> 00:26:36,120
