757
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:37,630
and skincare products for Aunt.

758
00:26:37,890 --> 00:26:39,080
You didn't have to bring

759
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:40,520
so much stuff.

760
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:41,490
It's the New Year.

761
00:26:41,490 --> 00:26:42,660
Gifts are a must.

762
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:44,250
It's only right.

763
00:26:44,250 --> 00:26:45,980
Aunt Yi, how's Grandpa doing?

764
00:26:46,970 --> 00:26:48,320
I tried to help him with medicine,

765
00:26:48,320 --> 00:26:49,160
but he was upset.

766
00:26:49,560 --> 00:26:50,900
"I want to rest. You go away."

767
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:52,490
You two go check on him.

768
00:26:52,490 --> 00:26:53,560
- Go check.
