769
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:55,260
I brought some tea for Grandpa.

770
00:26:55,520 --> 00:26:56,530
I'm going to see Grandpa.

771
00:26:56,530 --> 00:26:57,450
- Okay.
- Go ahead.

772
00:26:57,450 --> 00:26:58,290
Go ahead.

773
00:26:58,320 --> 00:26:59,550
