- Wait.

778
00:27:03,930 --> 00:27:05,120
After dinner, stay here, okay?

779
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:06,690
- There are empty rooms.
- Your hair.

780
00:27:06,690 --> 00:27:08,490
My brother has rooms next door.

781
00:27:08,490 --> 00:27:09,330
It's close by.

782
00:27:09,340 --> 00:27:10,270
Sounds good.

783
00:27:30,730 --> 00:27:31,570
Looks good.

784
00:27:37,650 --> 00:27:38,830
Good eye.

785
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:41,180
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

786
00:27:42,650 --> 00:27:44,180
Grandpa, Tang's here.

787
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:47,260
Grandpa, Happy New Year.

788
00:27:47,970 --> 00:27:49,360
Tang, Happy New Year.

789
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:50,220
Happy New Year.

790
00:27:50,410 --> 00:27:52,030
