791
00:27:54,120 --> 00:27:56,550
Wuyi Mountains Da Hong Pao tea.

792
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:58,180
Good tea, good tea.

793
00:27:58,410 --> 00:27:59,490
It's great for the heart

794
00:27:59,490 --> 00:28:00,650
