803
00:28:20,010 --> 00:28:20,890
Why are you laughing?

804
00:28:20,890 --> 00:28:21,940
You're still single too.

805
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:25,070
Fangping told me

806
00:28:25,250 --> 00:28:27,490
