807
00:28:27,490 --> 00:28:28,790
Where are you working now?

808
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:29,770
I'm currently...

809
00:28:29,770 --> 00:28:31,310
Jiang Shiyan, come start the fire.

810
00:28:31,730 --> 00:28:32,700
Coming, coming.

811
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:34,030
I'll go check.

812
00:28:35,320 --> 00:28:37,660
Grandpa, I'm working at a bank now.

813
00:28:38,080 --> 00:28:39,490
- Great.
- I work in CBBC.

814
00:28:39,490 --> 00:28:41,150
- Great.
- I'm a director now.

815
00:28:43,660 --> 00:28:44,500
Wonderful.

816
00:28:46,630 --> 00:28:47,470
Grandma.

