00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,420
Red envelopes, Grandma.

818
00:28:48,450 --> 00:28:49,290
Uncle.

819
00:28:49,410 --> 00:28:50,500
Jiang Shiyan.

820
00:28:50,730 --> 00:28:51,740
Jiang Shiyan.

821
00:28:51,890 --> 00:28:52,730
Look.

822
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:53,790
Look at this.

823
00:28:54,170 --> 00:28:55,010
