839
00:29:18,490 --> 00:29:19,420
or outdoors.

840
00:29:19,650 --> 00:29:20,940
- For me?
- Yes.

841
00:29:21,570 --> 00:29:22,460
Thank you.

842
00:29:22,470 --> 00:29:23,820
- Does it look good?
- Great.

843
00:29:23,840 --> 00:29:25,280
- It fits perfectly.
- Very nice.

844
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:26,880
