845
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,180
Why are you helping?

846
00:29:28,840 --> 00:29:29,980
How long since you last came?

847
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:31,360
Jiang Shiyan.

848
00:29:31,730 --> 00:29:33,970
Hurry up. Show her around.

849
00:29:33,970 --> 00:29:34,810
Alright.

850
00:29:34,970 --> 00:29:35,830
Well.

851
00:29:36,170 --> 00:29:37,030
Let me take that.

852
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:38,400
Let's go, let's go,

853
00:29:38,650 --> 00:29:40,010
